          <h1 class="story-title"><a href="/en/story/2020/06/1066852">WHO reports largest single day increase in COVID-19 cases</a></h1>
<div class="wrapper-date">
<div class="story-date pull-left"><span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2020-06-22T00:00:00-04:00">22 June 2020</span></div><span class="topics"><a href="/en/news/topic/health">Health</a></span><div class="sharethis pull-right"><div class="sharethis-wrapper"><span st_url="https://news.un.org/en/story/2020/06/1066852" st_title="WHO reports largest single day increase in COVID-19 cases" st_image="https://global.unitednations.entermediadb.net/assets/mediadb/services/module/asset/downloads/preset/Libraries/Production+Library/22-06-2020_UNICEF-I341019_India.jpg/image1024x768.jpg" class="st_pocket_custom" displayText="pocket"><span class="share-icon-label"></span></span>
<span st_url="https://news.un.org/en/story/2020/06/1066852" st_title="WHO reports largest single day increase in COVID-19 cases" st_image="https://global.unitednations.entermediadb.net/assets/mediadb/services/module/asset/downloads/preset/Libraries/Production+Library/22-06-2020_UNICEF-I341019_India.jpg/image1024x768.jpg" class="st_sharethis_custom" displayText="sharethis"><span class="share-icon-label"></span></span>
</div></div>
</div>
<div class="story-photo col-md-7 featured-media clearfix"><!-- scald=643322:un_news_large {"link":"node\/1066852"} --><a href="/en/story/2020/06/1066852"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://global.unitednations.entermediadb.net/assets/mediadb/services/module/asset/downloads/preset/Libraries/Production+Library/22-06-2020_UNICEF-I341019_India.jpg/image770x420cropped.jpg" title="A woman in Gujarat, India, is educated on the benefits of handwashing during the COVID-19 pandemic." width="747px" height="420px" /></a><div class="field-name-field-scald-photo-credit field field-name-scald-authors field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><span class="un-news-large scald-credit">© UNICEF/Vinay Panjwani</span></div><!-- END scald=643322 --></div>
<div class="col-md-5 news-body"><p>The World Health Organization (<a href="https://www.who.int/">WHO</a>) reported the largest single-day increase in coronavirus cases over the course of Sunday, registering more than 183,000 new infections in 24 hours, bringing the total to some 8.8 million cases worldwide, with more than 465,000 deaths.</p>

