<h1 class="story-title"><a href="/en/story/2020/06/1066742">On International Yoga Day, UN spotlights power of ancient practice to help ease COVID stress</a></h1>
<div class="wrapper-date">
<span class="topics"><a href="/en/news/topic/culture-and-education">Culture and Education</a></span><div class="sharethis pull-right"><div class="sharethis-wrapper"><span st_url="https://news.un.org/en/story/2020/06/1066742" st_title="On International Yoga Day, UN spotlights power of ancient practice to help ease COVID stress" st_image="https://global.unitednations.entermediadb.net/assets/mediadb/services/module/asset/downloads/preset/Libraries/Production+Library/18-06-2020-yoga-jon-witt-3.jpg/image1024x768.jpg" class="st_pocket_custom" displayText="pocket"><span class="share-icon-label"></span></span>
<span st_url="https://news.un.org/en/story/2020/06/1066742" st_title="On International Yoga Day, UN spotlights power of ancient practice to help ease COVID stress" st_image="https://global.unitednations.entermediadb.net/assets/mediadb/services/module/asset/downloads/preset/Libraries/Production+Library/18-06-2020-yoga-jon-witt-3.jpg/image1024x768.jpg" class="st_sharethis_custom" displayText="sharethis"><span class="share-icon-label"></span></span>
</div></div>
</div>
<div class="news-body"><p>The UN celebrates the sixth annual <a href="https://www.un.org/en/observances/yoga-day">International Day of Yoga</a> on 21 June, recognizing the ancient practice as a holistic approach to health and wellbeing, and a powerful tool for dealing with the myriad stresses brought on by the COVID-19 pandemic</p>
