<div class="body-wrapper">
<h1 class="story-title"><a href="/en/story/2020/06/1066532">FROM THE FIELD: the plight of refugees persecuted for their sexual orientation</a></h1>
<div class="wrapper-date">
<span class="topics"><a href="/en/news/topic/migrants-and-refugees">Migrants and Refugees</a></span><div class="sharethis pull-right"><div class="sharethis-wrapper"><span st_url="https://news.un.org/en/story/2020/06/1066532" st_title="FROM THE FIELD: the plight of refugees persecuted for their sexual orientation" st_image="https://global.unitednations.entermediadb.net/assets/mediadb/services/module/asset/downloads/preset/Libraries/Production+Library/17-06-20-Unsplash-Marseille-Pride-LGBTI.jpg/image1024x768.jpg" class="st_pocket_custom" displayText="pocket"><span class="share-icon-label"></span></span>
<span st_url="https://news.un.org/en/story/2020/06/1066532" st_title="FROM THE FIELD: the plight of refugees persecuted for their sexual orientation" st_image="https://global.unitednations.entermediadb.net/assets/mediadb/services/module/asset/downloads/preset/Libraries/Production+Library/17-06-20-Unsplash-Marseille-Pride-LGBTI.jpg/image1024x768.jpg" class="st_sharethis_custom" displayText="sharethis"><span class="share-icon-label"></span></span>
</div></div>
</div>
<div class="news-body"><p>Millions of people around the world are at risk because of their sexual orientation or sex characteristics. The UN refugee agency, UNHCR, has underlined the fact that, under international law, they must be protected as refugees. </p>
</div>
<div class="audio-bar"></div>
</div>
  </div>  </div>


  <div class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd clearfix">
      
